Map Features:

- 16 Players
- Protected Spawn (No Spawnkill anymore)
- AFK- and Spawncamper-Killer (20 Seconds time to leave Spawn)
- No Rush (240 Units, can be done with Strafe-LJ Skills ;) )
- Weapons: Knife, Desert Eagle, M4A1, AK-47 and one AWP for each side
- AWP has to be "earned"
- Long distance! (Aim well :) )
- Clear Textures (Thx to reacz!)
- Enemys are not that easy to see


This Map was made in hours. Don't expect some great work. I was bored and wanted to make an aim map for some friends!


Maybe you have fun with it! :)

Dotty
